latestPosts.caption:
23rd felt like 200 things happening in 24 hours.
There was light, then there wasn’t. Plans were made, paused, and remade. People came, some couldn’t. But somehow, between the cold, the chaos, and the change of plans—this birthday still found a way to feel warm.

Swipe, scroll, pause, watch. Because if there’s one thing this reel proves—it’s that joy is stubborn. And so am I.
